it.unibz.krdb.obda.owlrefplatform.owlapi3

Class QuestOWLStatement

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unibz.krdb.obda.owlrefplatform.owlapi3.QuestOWLStatement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    public class QuestOWLStatement
extends Object
implements AutoCloseable
    A Statement to execute queries over a QuestOWLConnection. The logic of this statement is equivalent to that of JDBC's Statements.

    Performance Note that you should not create multiple statements over the same connection to execute parallel queries (see QuestOWLConnection). Multiple statements over the same connection are not going to be very useful until we support updates (then statements will allow to implement transactions in the same way as JDBC Statements).

    Author:
    Mariano Rodriguez Muro
